    <id>https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/re-auto-deleted-line-items-of-pr/qaq-p/13654957/comment-id/4183338#M4183338</id>
    <title>Re: Auto Deleted Line Items of PR</title>
    <updated>2024-04-01T21:52:03.433000+02:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Prasoon</name>
      <uri>https://community.sap.com/t5/user/viewprofilepage/user-id/182900</uri>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;As mentioned in the note #&amp;nbsp;&lt;A title="2075110 - No change log for the deletion of requisitions created through MRP" href="https://me.sap.com/notes/2075110" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;2075110 - No change log for the deletion of requisitions created through MRP&lt;/A&gt;&amp;nbsp;, there is no change log in case the PR is deleted via MRP. You may check the PR creation indicator and confirm the same.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;If its manually created PR, you may check whether there is any custom program which is creating the issue.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Regards,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://community.sap.com/t5/enterprise-resource-planning-q-a/re-auto-deleted-line-items-of-pr/qaq-p/13654957/comment-id/4183338#M4183338"/>
    <published>2024-04-01T21:52:03.433000+02:00</published>
  </entry>
