    <content>&lt;P&gt;Hi experts,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;I have completed&lt;/SPAN&gt; &lt;A href="https://developers.sap.com/mission.sap-build-code-test-drive.html" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;SAP Build Code Test Drive&lt;/A&gt; tutorials. &lt;SPAN&gt;During the development process&lt;/SPAN&gt;, &lt;SPAN&gt;I noticed several files with the extension '.code'.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="MioYasuatke_0-1712004714636.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/89345i6101C11099799585/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="MioYasuatke_0-1712004714636.png" alt="MioYasuatke_0-1712004714636.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Could you please clarify the purpose of these files and the potential consequences of editing or removing them?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;pre class="lia-code-sample language-json"&gt;&lt;code&gt;{
    "version": "2.0",
    "codes": [],
    "configuration": {
        "phase": "on",
        "events": [
            "CREATE"
        ],
        "entity": "loyaltyProgramSrv.Purchases"
    },
    "hash": "710aa051dcacd2609053c4d3517c688c4b4792abad4454d7bc203bfd5f6b5a56ef7e620d7e7db9ad922c7c6eae302cc6fc98da704728746cdc31459744fe5dd8"
}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;P&gt;Best regards,&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;Mio Yasutake&lt;/P&gt;</content>
