    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Hi everyone, &lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;I am trying to extend one Fiori App (Close Evolotion) in SAP S4HANA Financial Closing Cockpit. I want to add a company code.&amp;nbsp;I want to parse the processor area and use it, but can you share a best practice and the document about the next steps after extending the CDS?&amp;nbsp;Is there any obstacle to extending this CDS?&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ertugrul_0-1712010192378.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/89378iD941155207A92CF9/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ertugrul_0-1712010192378.png" alt="ertugrul_0-1712010192378.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ertugrul_1-1712010244514.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/89380iDD7BA0595681294A/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ertugrul_1-1712010244514.png" alt="ertugrul_1-1712010244514.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ertugrul_5-1712010851426.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/89391i95EB70C64A7CC249/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ertugrul_5-1712010851426.png" alt="ertugrul_5-1712010851426.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ertugrul_3-1712010476576.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/89387iD8251D10494A9FAA/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ertugrul_3-1712010476576.png" alt="ertugrul_3-1712010476576.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;In cube, this field appears in the comments. Opening it may also be an option. If we need to do association, we can consider that too?&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="ertugrul_4-1712010499998.png" style="width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/89388i6C2ABF90F89D5E33/image-size/medium/is-moderation-mode/true?v=v2&amp;amp;px=400" role="button" title="ertugrul_4-1712010499998.png" alt="ertugrul_4-1712010499998.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
